<plot>Every morning the table is laid afresh, and the children of misfortune gather- like clockwork. A short film about a ceremony conducted in the purgatory of our dreams, "The Persian Love Cake" explores the cruelty of a game. The line between formality and savagery erodes when nature literally conquers, dictating the fate of the players.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?582251</url></doc>
